00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:21,760
♪Evening breeze cradles verdant hills♪

2
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:27,140
♪Embracing the waves of the deep sea♪

3
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:33,670
♪Paper kites aim for distant shores♪

4
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:37,400
♪Together, we conclude our tale♪

5
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:38,520
[Land of Dreams]

6
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:41,340
[Episode 6]

7
00:00:41,860 --> 00:00:43,660
Our gang has recruited a new assassin.

8
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:44,860
I want you to instruct her.

9
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:05,300
Qingming,

10
00:01:05,860 --> 00:01:06,620
I'm surprised.

11
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:09,180
You were tailed by her.

12
00:01:10,060 --> 00:01:11,700
She followed you
to the Blood Sacrifice Gang.

13
00:01:12,020 --> 00:01:14,340
She is Guyu, your new disciple.

14
00:01:15,660 --> 00:01:18,380
You guys should
get to know each other better.

15
00:01:23,020 --> 00:01:25,620
Master, it's good to see you again.

16
00:01:26,260 --> 00:01:27,380
Again?

17
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:36,260
Again?

18
00:01:39,740 --> 00:01:40,540
Mengchen,

19
00:01:42,460 --> 00:01:43,340
what are you doing here?

20
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:44,060
Come home with me.

21
00:01:44,060 --> 00:01:44,900
Hurry, come home with me.

22
00:01:47,140 --> 00:01:47,980
Mengchen?

23
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:53,580
We met once outside the workshop
that day.

24
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:55,980
We resemble each other a bit.

25
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:58,060
I just didn't expect

26
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:00,780
even as her brother,

27
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,460
you mistake someone else for her.

28
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:06,540
Master,

29
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:09,620
which do you think

30
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:11,420
is prettier,

31
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:13,900
me or your sister?

32
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:16,020
How similar are we, really?

33
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:17,900
Take a closer look.

34
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:20,060
I'm curious, too.

35
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:29,540
Since we're so alike,

36
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:34,860
could you treat me as a sister, too?

37
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:44,060
You're not Mengchen.

38
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:47,220
I wish I were.

39
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:49,060
To have a brother's love

40
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:50,780
and a home to return to

41
00:02:51,420 --> 00:02:54,100
means not having to struggle so hard
to make a living alone.

42
00:02:59,340 --> 00:03:00,140
Master,

43
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:04,540
would you mind having another sister?

44
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:12,940
Brother,

45
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:15,860
I promise I'll be good.

46
00:03:20,020 --> 00:03:20,940
Starting tomorrow,

47
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:23,220
when the Blood Sacrifice Gang needs you,

48
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,500
we will naturally summon you.

49
00:03:32,570 --> 00:03:34,370
[Tongji Dyeing Workshop]

50
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,620
[Fengchun Theater]

51
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:32,420
What does the Blood Sacrifice Gang want?

52
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:35,580
Didn't you promise not
to inquire about my origins or pasts?

53
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:37,180
Why follow me?

54
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:40,820
If you truly don't trust me,
whether to kill or maim me,

55
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:42,220
I am at your disposal.

56
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:45,460
This has nothing to do with the Gang.

57
00:04:49,140 --> 00:04:51,860
So, it's because I tailed you.

58
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,540
You wanted to probe

59
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:54,900
and get leverage on me.

60
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:57,700
Or is it,

61
00:04:59,420 --> 00:05:00,700
Master,

62
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,980
you have other intentions toward me?

63
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:24,180
People say

64
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:25,660
a tear mole

65
00:05:26,180 --> 00:05:29,100
is the sprout of this life's hardships
on the face.

66
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:33,860
A woman with a tear mole

67
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,780
is destined to be alone

68
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:38,780
and drift through her whole life.

69
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:42,620
Are you an opera singer here?

70
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:46,700
My parents died early,

71
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:48,740
so I joined the troupe.

72
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,920
♪Fate entwined♪

73
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:55,400
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

74
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:58,180
♪My sorrow overwhelmed♪

75
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,620
Why did you join
the Blood Sacrifice Gang?

76
00:06:03,540 --> 00:06:04,940
Obviously, for money.

77
00:06:05,740 --> 00:06:07,020
I want to buy my freedom

78
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:08,780
to make a clean break with the past.

79
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:12,140
Do you know

80
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:14,740
joining the Gang means
risking your life to earn money?

81
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,220
Yes.

82
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:20,460
As long as the pay is good.

83
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:21,580
It's very dangerous.

84
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:25,380
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

85
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,220
♪My sorrow overwhelmed♪

86
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:32,380
♪I gaze at the moon, longing for you♪

87
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:34,300
Then, Master,

88
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:37,100
would you be willing to protect me?

89
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:43,740
She really isn't Mengchen.

90
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:53,180
♪In this fleeting dream,
love remains forever without regrets♪

91
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:05,700
Go.

92
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:07,740
Flick.

93
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:13,420
Collect.

94
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:18,300
Sleeves. Take a bow.

95
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:24,500
You're quite bright.

96
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:25,780
You're picking this up so quickly.

97
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,300
I owe you my thanks, Miss Qiaomei,

98
00:07:28,660 --> 00:07:30,540
for lending me your identity.

99
00:07:31,460 --> 00:07:32,900
No need for formalities.

100
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:34,820
If it weren't for your
righteous intervention that day,

101
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:37,780
our troupe might have already been
plundered by villains.

102
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:40,100
By the way, what are you intending to do?

103
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:40,940
What am I doing?

104
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:48,260
I want to be a heroine

105
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:49,900
who upholds justice

106
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:53,580
and spreads the supreme heroism.

107
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:00,340
Tell me

108
00:08:00,900 --> 00:08:02,100
who sent you here?

109
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,380
I followed someone here.

110
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:05,660
Who were you following?

111
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:07,380
What's your purpose in coming here?

112
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:11,020
If I were afraid at the sight of a knife,

113
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:14,100
how could I dare to come here
to become an assassin?

114
00:08:15,860 --> 00:08:17,260
You want to become an assassin?

115
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:24,020
Miss Qiaomei,
it's time for you to go on stage.

116
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:26,700
Got it.

117
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:33,700
Hasn't Miss Qiaomei shown herself?

118
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:46,660
Great!

119
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,060
She's finally here.

120
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,820
Nice!

121
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:52,140
Her debut is truly something special.

122
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:59,500
In the dimming desert, the sun sets west.

123
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:03,620
Warhorses neigh,

124
00:09:06,220 --> 00:09:08,180
hunger in their chest.

125
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:12,300
For paths are secret, steps discreet.

126
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:15,620
The border's in sight.

127
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:17,060
Great!

128
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:18,580
Fantastic!

129
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:24,070
[Nanyan Residence]

130
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:28,260
Mengchen.

131
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,300
Mengchen.

132
00:09:35,740 --> 00:09:36,580
Brother,

133
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:38,100
it's so late.

134
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:39,620
What's up?

135
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:42,540
Just checking

136
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:44,060
if you were asleep.

137
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:46,580
I've been asleep.

138
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,220
I waited for you all night.

139
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:52,620
Oh, there are some red bean cakes
I made in the kitchen.

140
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:53,820
Do you want to try them?

141
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,540
They're pretty bad, though.

142
00:09:57,220 --> 00:09:59,300
I wanted to wait for you to teach me.

143
00:09:59,300 --> 00:10:00,700
But you didn't come back.

144
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:02,140
So I made them myself.

145
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,620
You made red bean cakes yourself?

146
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:08,500
If you wanted to eat,
you should've just told me.

147
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:09,300
I could make some for you.

148
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:10,860
Okay.

149
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:15,020
I'm off to bed then.

150
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:17,060
Go ahead.

151
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:31,540
Bravo!

152
00:10:31,540 --> 00:10:32,340
Great!

153
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:33,540
Wonderful!

154
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:35,660
Fantastic!

155
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:49,740
Fantastic!

156
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:51,100
Fantastic!

157
00:11:13,180 --> 00:11:13,980
Not bad.

158
00:11:33,540 --> 00:11:35,420
Are you okay? Why didn't you dodge?

159
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:40,420
Master, you care about me so much?

160
00:11:45,180 --> 00:11:46,140
Stop training for now.

161
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:48,860
I'll show you around the Gang.
Come with me.

162
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:04,740
These are all people killed
by the Blood Sacrifice Gang.

163
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:07,980
Although we're an assassin's gang,

164
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:09,860
we absolutely do not kill the innocent
without reason.

165
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:12,460
These people took lives,

166
00:12:12,460 --> 00:12:13,500
dealt in opium,

167
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:14,460
and dominated some areas.

168
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:17,820
Seems like they all got
what they deserved.

169
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:20,300
We always thoroughly investigate
our clients

170
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:21,420
and their crimes for every mission.

171
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:23,920
[Lin Yueniang, Lin Yucheng, Lin Chu]

172
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:29,540
What crimes did the three people commit?

173
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:31,460
They poisoned villagers.

174
00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:34,100
Then why place their names here?

175
00:12:37,180 --> 00:12:39,140
The client for this mission disappeared.

176
00:12:39,340 --> 00:12:42,180
And it's also a mission
I've yet to complete.

177
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:46,260
It's your mission?

178
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:48,860
Yes.

179
00:12:57,490 --> 00:13:03,120
♪A glance seals our fate♪

180
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:09,840
♪Without you, time fades into night♪

181
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:16,430
♪My heart adrift,
seeking wings to break free♪

182
00:13:17,970 --> 00:13:22,830
♪Through tears, our love endures♪

183
00:13:23,470 --> 00:13:26,420
♪Fate entwined♪

184
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:29,170
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

185
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:32,050
♪My sorrow overwhelmed♪

186
00:13:32,050 --> 00:13:36,150
♪I gaze at the moon, longing for you♪

187
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:39,220
♪Love as vast as stars♪

188
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:43,510
♪In the galaxy,
I yearn for your presence♪

189
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:52,280
♪In this fleeting dream,
love remains forever without regrets♪
